    - Volume Explosion:    20% weight (raw 0-30, normalized) [was 30%]
    - Volatility (ATR%):   15% weight (raw 0-25, normalized) [was 20%]
    - Float Tightness:     15% weight (raw 0-20, normalized) [was 20%]
